{
  "id": 5190778418757632,
  "name": "Cookie Store API `maxAge` attribute",
  "summary": "Allows callers to specify a `maxAge` when setting a cookie with the Cookie Store API.\n\nCookie expiry time is already configurable using the `expires` attribute, but `maxAge` provides a more idiomatic option and aligns the Cookie Store API with the options provided by `document.cookie` and the `Set-Cookie` HTTP Header.  ",
